    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――デザイン会社にて",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "このマネキンが着ているのが\n今度のライブで着る新衣装の試作品なんですね",
      "startTime": 4.9769246802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "とっても綺麗で素敵なドレスですね\nただ、私にはちょっと大人っぽ過ぎるかも……",
      "startTime": 12.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今回の衣装は、さくらが大人っぽいデザインを\n希望したんだよな？",
      "startTime": 20.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、やってみたかったリストに「大人っぽい\n綺麗なドレスを着る」というのがあって……",
      "startTime": 26.0916329067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "それを実現するチャンスだと思って\n思い切ってお願いしてみたんです",
      "startTime": 31.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さくらがやりたいことをノートにまとめた\n『やってみたかったリスト』か……",
      "startTime": 37.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "だから、大人っぽい衣装を着るのは\n私がやりたかったことなんですけど……",
      "startTime": 42.575579548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "こうして実際に見ると\n子供っぽい私には似合わない気がして……",
      "startTime": 47.875579548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはないと思うが……おっと、そろそろ時間だ\n俺は次の現場に行くが、さくらはこの後どうするんだ？",
      "startTime": 56.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "私はこの後、遙子ちゃんと合流して\n登山用の靴を買いに行く予定です",
      "startTime": 64.2186639151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "やってみたかったリストに「山のてっぺんから\nヤッホーと叫ぶ」というのがあって……",
      "startTime": 69.8139487246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "そのことを遙子ちゃんに話したら、山登りについて\nレクチャーしてもらえることになったんです",
      "startTime": 76.8153018113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……いろんなことに挑戦するのはいいが\nあまり無理はするなよ",
      "startTime": 83.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6607.393900600002,
          "startTime": 89.8073939006
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4266.66666669999,
          "startTime": 87.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "糸を掛けて、抜いて……あれ？　ここ、間違えてる\nせっかくここまで編んだのに、ほどいてやり直しだよ～",
      "startTime": 95.1469665212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さくら？　一人で何をしているんだ？\nそれは……編み物？",
      "startTime": 104.1000030518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "はい、やってみたかったリストの「手編みのマフラーを\n好きな人にプレゼントする」に挑戦してるんです",
      "startTime": 111.538599237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "編み物が得意な千紗ちゃんから\nマフラーの編み方を教わったんですよ",
      "startTime": 117.4719325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、好きな人にマフラーを……好きな人！？\nい、一体、誰にプレゼントする気なんだ！？",
      "startTime": 124.8666697185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんにあげるつもりです。マフラーを編むのは\n初めてなので、ちゃんと出来るか分からないですけど",
      "startTime": 131.6968989057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "お父さん……そ、そうか……好きってそういう……\n心配しなくてもさくらの手編みなら絶対喜んでくれるさ",
      "startTime": 142.2148967591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、{user}さんは\n普段、マフラーをしないですよね",
      "startTime": 148.8206402145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "以前はしていたんだが、人にあげてしまってな\nだから今はしていないんだ",
      "startTime": 155.6666697185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "マフラーを持ってないんですか？\nそうなんだ……",
      "startTime": 160.7789399786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、最近よく『やってみたかったリスト』に\n挑戦しているが、何か理由でもあるのか？",
      "startTime": 166.6333363851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "実は、友ちゃんが書いた『やってみたかったリスト』を\n最近、いただいたんです",
      "startTime": 174.1085125927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "友ちゃんって、さくらが入院していた頃の友達だよな？",
      "startTime": 176.0594621179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "はい……友ちゃんは、「私がやりたいことだから\n気にしないで」って書いてくれてたんですけど……",
      "startTime": 185.3268122041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ友ちゃんの誕生日なので、それまでに\n一つでも多く実現してあげたいと思ったんです",
      "startTime": 192.2268122041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "一昨日は葵ちゃんに教わってケーキ作りに挑戦して\n昨日はkanaさんに英会話を教えてもらおうと……",
      "startTime": 200.8268122041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "「なんでさくらにまで教えなきゃいけないの」って\n渋るkanaさんにお願いしてたんです",
      "startTime": 208.1174898521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_01-skr021.m4a",
      "text": "他にもいろいろ挑戦していて……でも、実現するのが\n難しいものもあって、結構苦戦してるんです",
      "startTime": 216.8268122041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
